### Enrichment
Dagre v3.0.0 was published recently (April 2026), indicating the project is actively maintained again. Only the @dagrejs/dagre scoped package on npm receives updates. Key alternative: ELK.js offers more layout options but is heavier. Dagre has 61.5k+ dependents. For beestgraph visualization, dagre remains the best lightweight choice for directed graph layout.

